name: Naked News Uncovered
overview: A funny behind the scenes series about Naked News as they battle to regain their former glory.

episodes.name: Peter and the Gauntlet
episodes.overview: The owner of Naked News throws down the gauntlet that big changes must be made in order to survive. Meanwhile, a Halloween cooking shoot goes awry when best friends and anchors, Rachelle and Peyton, drink too much champagne.

episodes.name: Who Screwed Up Halloween?
episodes.overview: Superstorm Sandy hits and Eila Adams reports on it in a bizarre Halloween costume. A new marketing VP arrives and organizes a focus group with unexpected results.

episodes.name: The Rise and Fall of the Ass-Cam
episodes.overview: A bizarre "butt camera" test shoot yields dubious results, while "frenemies" Rachel and Erica head out into the streets for a potentially explosive shoot.

episodes.name: The Girl with the Butterfly Tattoo
episodes.overview: Staff are challenged to cover the US election in a fresh way and a potential anchor, with a secret to hide, is auditioned.

episodes.name: The Work Jerks
episodes.overview: Sparks fly when a former failed staffer returns to Naked News to create a new opening theme, while two writers compete to direct fresh naked segments.

episodes.name: Crazy/Beautiful
episodes.overview: Naked News hires a new publicist while Lucas juggles 10 different anchors and their neuroses over beauty and aging, until one anchor 'goes nuclear' forcing Lucas to make a critical decision.

episodes.name: Naked Is Easy/Comedy Is Hard Pt.1
episodes.overview: Naked News' new publicist creates a naked stand-up comedy event which, come show time, leads to mass chaos.
